{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, how do we ensure that the assessment criteria apply equally to native and non-native speakers, given the requirement to use English creatively?",
    "These are highly relevant questions.",
    "With respect to the former, we responded that the module allows students to forge such links to techniques of writing and unleash their creativity; both writing and translation entail considering alternatives, generate many ideas and select the most relevant one for each situation, using the tools given in each session.",
    "Looking at alternative versions of texts (i.e.",
    "texts they have been working on throughout the module) in particular hones their expressional fluency."
  ]
}